{"tid":2115761,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"『薪火post』BNO 續期資訊(93) DARKEST HOUR","createTime":"2020-07-19T17:54:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T17:57:12.000Z","uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9fee819b9b123d7aadac8cad5adf938b2e3340c5","tid":2115761,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T17:54:00.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mh9kwRG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fmh9kwRG.jpg&h=64cc38c5&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>BNO新系統連登特色佛系續期精神</strong></span></span></strong></p><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\"><strong>&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;請新入嚟嘅巴絲打睇完Google Docs後唔明先問問題&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;</strong></span></span></strong></p><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1sccskS5ZN9vRZveWFRS0vneBNO5Fk8csOKj3H2s3sdU/edit?pli=1#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1sccskS5ZN9vRZveWFRS0vneBNO5Fk8csOKj3H2s3sdU%2Fedit%3Fpli%3D1%23&d=WPu%2B6xJKQhRrkkmyce%2F8pg2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=9b9de640\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1sccskS5ZN9vRZveWFRS0vneBNO5Fk8csOKj3H2s3sdU/edit?pli=1#</a><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xXp8Xjz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxXp8Xjz.png&h=4a619eda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ElAtJX7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FElAtJX7.png&h=9ceee922&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><ins>持有 Certificate of Registration as a British Citizen 的第一次申請 British Citizen 護照人士，請發文查詢方法。如使用錯誤方法作第一次申請，可能要比錢作第二次申請。</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n申請續領英國國民海外護照（British National Overseas (BNO)） <br />\n<br />\n（不適用於身處英國本土人士續領。以下文件清單為香港續領而設。如你於香港及英國以外地方續領，文件的要求或者申請方式可能有所不同，你可以瀏覽英國政府網站查閱身處地之確實申請方法）<br />\n<br />\n詳情或申請流程請參閱以下由<strong>卡斐帕西飛</strong> &amp; <strong>郭藹明日香</strong>製作既doc，由連登會員 <strong>希魔</strong> 所更新，<span class=\"xx-large\">一般既疑問應該係呢份doc度答哂大家</span>。睇完之後有問題嘅話歡迎提問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\">續領BN(O)詳細google document:</span></span></strong>(有關單次使用的緊急護照申請方法包含在內)<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1sccskS5ZN9vRZveWFRS0vneBNO5Fk8csOKj3H2s3sdU/edit?pli=1#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1sccskS5ZN9vRZveWFRS0vneBNO5Fk8csOKj3H2s3sdU%2Fedit%3Fpli%3D1%23&d=WPu%2B6xJKQhRrkkmyce%2F8pg2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=9b9de640\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1sccskS5ZN9vRZveWFRS0vneBNO5Fk8csOKj3H2s3sdU/edit?pli=1#</a></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\">如閣下想到英國工作，請搜尋 英倫扮工室 POST</span></span></strong></p><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\">另外希望使用新系統申請嘅巴打可以喺 post 度分享返整個申請流程，以便巴打更新返份 doc</span></span></strong></p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>最後更新 : 2020年6月12日</strong>"},{"pid":"f51ae443d47bb73318c3a8925badc214f0355f25","tid":2115761,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T17:57:12.000Z","msg":"『薪火post』BNO 續期資訊(94) DARKEST HOUR<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2115765\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2115765</a>"}],"pinned":{"pid":"f51ae443d47bb73318c3a8925badc214f0355f25","tid":2115761,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T17:57:12.000Z","msg":"『薪火post』BNO 續期資訊(94) DARKEST HOUR<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2115765\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2115765</a>"}}